<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Slide 10 - Atenciones y Horas Diarias</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #eef4fb;
    }

    .s10-slide {
      width: 1600px;
      height: 900px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f4f8ff 100%);
      color: #08245c;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      padding: 22px 26px 0 26px;
    }

    .s10-bottom-band {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #082d91 0%, #0d65df 55%, #13b7ba 100%);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .s10-header {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      height: 66px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding-right: 360px;
    }

    .s10-title-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .s10-title-bar {
      width: 13px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0d65df, #13b7ba);
    }

    .s10-title {
      font-size: 38px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #071f5c;
      letter-spacing: -0.7px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .s10-kpi-row {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .s10-kpi-card {
      height: 122px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #d2dceb;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(11,45,92,0.16);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 84px 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
    }

    .s10-kpi-icon {
      width: 72px;
      height: 72px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: 0 9px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
    }

    .s10-bg-blue {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1264df, #06339b);
    }

    .s10-bg-teal {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1ac4c6, #087a87);
    }

    .s10-bg-orange {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffb51d, #ff5f00);
    }

    .s10-bg-purple {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9542e8, #5520aa);
    }

    .s10-kpi-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #092869;
      line-height: 1.15;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
    }

    .s10-kpi-value {
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      color: #0d55d8;
    }

    .s10-teal {
      color: #0a8a96;
    }

    .s10-orange {
      color: #ff6200;
    }

    .s10-purple {
      color: #7a35d7;
    }

    .s10-chart-panel {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      height: 474px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #cddbef;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(11,45,92,0.16);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .s10-panel-title {
      height: 39px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0b3298 0%, #0d5dd4 50%, #11b7bb 100%);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding-left: 24px;
      font-size: 19px;
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }

    .s10-chart-box {
      height: 435px;
      padding: 6px 28px 4px 28px;
    }

    .s10-bottom-grid {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.38fr 0.62fr;
      gap: 18px;
      height: 152px;
    }

    .s10-summary-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1.7px solid #1b65e3;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(11,45,92,0.10);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 112px 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 22px 24px;
    }

    .s10-summary-icon {
      width: 76px;
      height: 76px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d65df, #13b7ba);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(11,45,92,0.20);
    }

    .s10-summary-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #092d91;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .s10-summary-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: #0a1b44;
    }

    .s10-insights-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06349d 0%, #0d65df 48%, #12b6b9 100%);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(11,45,92,0.18);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 88px 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 28px;
      color: white;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .s10-insight-main-icon {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #0b3298;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
    }

    .s10-insights-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .s10-insight-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .s10-check-icon {
      width: 25px;
      height: 25px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #0d55d8;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .s10-insight-text {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.22;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .s10-insight-divider {
      height: 1px;
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      margin: 4px 0 10px 44px;
    }

    .s10-axis-label {
      fill: #08245c;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .s10-axis-title {
      fill: #08245c;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .s10-bar-label-dark {
      fill: #ffffff;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .s10-bar-label-light {
      fill: #0a1b44;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .s10-date-label {
      fill: #08245c;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .s10-legend-text {
      fill: #08245c;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<%
  function num(v) {
    return Number(v) || 0;
  }

  const rawDias = typeof dias !== 'undefined' && Array.isArray(dias)
    ? dias
    : [];

  const data = rawDias.map(d => ({
    fecha: d.fecha || d.dia || '',
    dia: d.dia || d.fecha || '',
    atenciones: num(d.atenciones),
    horas: num(d.horas)
  })).filter(d => d.fecha || d.dia);

  const totalAt = num(
    typeof totalAtenciones !== 'undefined'
      ? totalAtenciones
      : data.reduce((a, b) => a + b.atenciones, 0)
  );

  const totalHr = num(
    typeof totalHoras !== 'undefined'
      ? totalHoras
      : data.reduce((a, b) => a + b.horas, 0)
  );

  const diasActivos = num(
    typeof diasConAtencion !== 'undefined'
      ? diasConAtencion
      : typeof diasPeriodo !== 'undefined'
        ? diasPeriodo
        : data.length
  );

  const promedioAt = typeof promedioAtencionesDia !== 'undefined'
    ? promedioAtencionesDia
    : diasActivos ? (totalAt / diasActivos).toFixed(1) : '0.0';

  const promedioHr = typeof promedioHorasDia !== 'undefined'
    ? promedioHorasDia
    : diasActivos ? (totalHr / diasActivos).toFixed(1) : '0.0';

  const horasAt = typeof horasPorAtencion !== 'undefined'
    ? horasPorAtencion
    : totalAt ? (totalHr / totalAt).toFixed(2) : '0.00';

  const safePeriodo = typeof periodo !== 'undefined'
    ? periodo
    : 'Marzo 2026';

  const safeTitulo = typeof titulo !== 'undefined'
    ? titulo
    : 'ATENCIONES EN LA OPERACIÓN YAURICOCHA - ' + String(safePeriodo).toUpperCase();

  const safeInsights = typeof insights !== 'undefined' && Array.isArray(insights) && insights.length
    ? insights
    : [
        'La distribución diaria evidencia el comportamiento operativo del periodo seleccionado.',
        'El seguimiento diario permite identificar picos de demanda y asignar recursos con mayor precisión.'
      ];

  const maxStackRaw = Math.max(...data.map(d => d.atenciones + d.horas), 1);
  const maxStack = Math.ceil(maxStackRaw / 5) * 5;

  const chartLeft = 70;
  const chartTop = 24;
  const chartW = 1400;
  const chartH = 290;
  const baseY = chartTop + chartH;
  const gap = data.length ? chartW / data.length : chartW;
  const barW = Math.min(28, gap * 0.55);
%>

<div class="s10-slide">
  <div class="s10-bottom-band"></div>

  <div class="s10-header">
    <div class="s10-title-wrap">
      <div class="s10-title-bar"></div>
      <div class="s10-title"><%= safeTitulo %></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="s10-kpi-row">
    <div class="s10-kpi-card">
      <div class="s10-kpi-icon s10-bg-blue">▣</div>
      <div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-label">Días</div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-value"><%= diasActivos %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="s10-kpi-card">
      <div class="s10-kpi-icon s10-bg-teal">●●●</div>
      <div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-label">Atenciones</div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-value s10-teal"><%= totalAt %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="s10-kpi-card">
      <div class="s10-kpi-icon s10-bg-blue">◷</div>
      <div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-label">Horas</div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-value"><%= totalHr %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="s10-kpi-card">
      <div class="s10-kpi-icon s10-bg-orange">▥</div>
      <div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-label">Promedio de<br>Atenciones por Día</div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-value s10-orange"><%= promedioAt %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="s10-kpi-card">
      <div class="s10-kpi-icon s10-bg-purple">◷</div>
      <div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-label">Promedio de<br>Horas por Día</div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-value s10-purple"><%= promedioHr %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="s10-kpi-card">
      <div class="s10-kpi-icon s10-bg-teal">▦</div>
      <div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-label">Horas por<br>Atención</div>
        <div class="s10-kpi-value s10-teal"><%= horasAt %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="s10-chart-panel">
    <div class="s10-panel-title">ATENCIONES Y HORAS DIARIAS - <%= String(safePeriodo).toUpperCase() %></div>

    <div class="s10-chart-box">
      <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 1500 410" preserveAspectRatio="none">

        <% [0, 0.25, 0.50, 0.75, 1].forEach(p => {
          const y = baseY - p * chartH;
          const val = Math.round(maxStack * p);
        %>
          <line
            x1="<%= chartLeft %>"
            y1="<%= y %>"
            x2="<%= chartLeft + chartW %>"
            y2="<%= y %>"
            stroke="#d6dde8"
            stroke-width="1"
            stroke-dasharray="4 4"
          ></line>

          <text x="42" y="<%= y + 5 %>" class="s10-axis-label"><%= val %></text>
        <% }) %>

        <text x="20" y="190" transform="rotate(-90 20,190)" class="s10-axis-title">
          CANTIDAD
        </text>

        <% data.forEach((item, i) => {
          const xCenter = chartLeft + i * gap + gap / 2;
          const atH = maxStack ? (item.atenciones / maxStack) * chartH : 0;
          const hrH = maxStack ? (item.horas / maxStack) * chartH : 0;

          const x = xCenter - barW / 2;
          const atY = baseY - atH;
          const hrY = baseY - atH - hrH;
        %>
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="s10GradAt<%= i %>" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0d65df"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#07349f"/>
            </linearGradient>

            <linearGradient id="s10GradHr<%= i %>" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#b9d7ff"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8dbaff"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>

          <rect
            x="<%= x %>"
            y="<%= hrY %>"
            width="<%= barW %>"
            height="<%= hrH %>"
            fill="url(#s10GradHr<%= i %>)"
            rx="2"
          ></rect>

          <rect
            x="<%= x %>"
            y="<%= atY %>"
            width="<%= barW %>"
            height="<%= atH %>"
            fill="url(#s10GradAt<%= i %>)"
            rx="2"
          ></rect>

          <% if (item.horas > 0) { %>
            <text
              x="<%= xCenter %>"
              y="<%= hrY + Math.max(14, hrH / 2) %>"
              text-anchor="middle"
              class="s10-bar-label-light"
            >
              <%= item.horas %>
            </text>
          <% } %>

          <% if (item.atenciones > 0) { %>
            <text
              x="<%= xCenter %>"
              y="<%= atY + Math.max(15, atH / 2 + 4) %>"
              text-anchor="middle"
              class="s10-bar-label-dark"
            >
              <%= item.atenciones %>
            </text>
          <% } %>

          <text
            x="<%= xCenter %>"
            y="345"
            text-anchor="end"
            transform="rotate(-48 <%= xCenter %>,345)"
            class="s10-date-label"
          >
            <%= item.fecha || item.dia %>
          </text>
        <% }) %>

        <line
          x1="<%= chartLeft %>"
          y1="<%= baseY %>"
          x2="<%= chartLeft + chartW %>"
          y2="<%= baseY %>"
          stroke="#c5cfdf"
          stroke-width="2"
        ></line>

        <rect x="635" y="383" width="14" height="14" fill="#0b43bf"></rect>
        <text x="660" y="397" class="s10-legend-text">Atenciones</text>

        <rect x="830" y="383" width="14" height="14" fill="#9fc6ff"></rect>
        <text x="855" y="397" class="s10-legend-text">Horas</text>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="s10-bottom-grid">
    <div class="s10-summary-card">
      <div class="s10-summary-icon">↗</div>

      <div>
        <div class="s10-summary-title">Tendencia de Atenciones Diarias</div>
        <div class="s10-summary-text">
          Distribución diaria de atenciones, mostrando estabilidad operativa y picos controlados de demanda a lo largo del mes.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="s10-insights-card">
      <div class="s10-insight-main-icon">●</div>

      <div>
        <div class="s10-insights-title">INSIGHTS EJECUTIVOS</div>

        <div class="s10-insight-row">
          <div class="s10-check-icon">✓</div>
          <div class="s10-insight-text">
            <%= safeInsights[0] || 'La distribución diaria evidencia el comportamiento operativo del periodo seleccionado.' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="s10-insight-divider"></div>

        <div class="s10-insight-row">
          <div class="s10-check-icon">✓</div>
          <div class="s10-insight-text">
            <%= safeInsights[1] || 'El seguimiento diario permite identificar picos de demanda y asignar recursos con mayor precisión.' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
